WITH cte_sequence AS (
  SELECT 
    DATEADD(DAY,value, CAST('2020-01-01' AS DATE)) AS d
  FROM GENERATE_SERIES ( 
    0
    , DATEDIFF(DAY, CAST('2020-01-01' AS DATE)
    , DATEADD(YEAR, 5
    , 
    CAST('2024-10-06 19:45:56' AS DATE)
))
    , 1
    ) AS gs
),

cte_core_definition AS (
  SELECT
    date_standard                        = CONVERT(DATE,d)
    , date_int                           = FORMAT(CONVERT(DATE,d), 'yyyyMMdd')
    , day_of_month_number                = DATEPART(DAY,d)
    , day_of_week_number                 = DATEPART(WEEKDAY,d)
    , first_date_of_month                = DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(d),MONTH(d),1)
    , last_date_of_month                 = DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(d),MONTH(d),DAY(EOMONTH(d)))
    , is_current_day                     = IIF(CONVERT(DATE,d) =  
    CAST('2024-10-06 19:45:56' AS DATE)
, 1, 0)
    , is_above_current_day               = IIF(CONVERT(DATE,d) >  
    CAST('2024-10-06 19:45:56' AS DATE)
, 1, 0)
    , is_above_or_at_current_day         = IIF(CONVERT(DATE,d) >= 
    CAST('2024-10-06 19:45:56' AS DATE)
, 1, 0)
    , calendar_year_number               = DATEPART(YEAR,d)
    , calendar_first_day_of_year         = DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(d),1,1)
    , calendar_last_day_of_year          = DATEFROMPARTS(YEAR(d),12,31)
    , calendar_month_of_year_number      = DATEPART(MONTH,d)
    , fiscal_year_number                 = CASE WHEN DATEPART(MONTH,d) >= 2 THEN DATEPART(YEAR,d) ELSE DATEPART(YEAR,d) - 1 END
    , fiscal_first_day_of_year           = DATEFROMPARTS(CASE WHEN DATEPART(MONTH,d) >= 2 THEN DATEPART(YEAR,d) ELSE DATEPART(YEAR,d) - 1 END, 2, 1)
    , fiscal_last_day_of_year            = DATEADD(DAY, -1, DATEFROMPARTS(CASE WHEN DATEPART(MONTH,d) >= 2 THEN DATEPART(YEAR,d) + 1 ELSE DATEPART(YEAR,d) END, 2, 1))
    , fiscal_month_of_year_number        = (DATEPART(MONTH,d) + 12 - 2) % 12 + 1
  FROM cte_sequence
),

                    cast("transaction_status" as varchar(16)) as "transaction_status" ,

                    cast("expected_delivery_date" as varchar(16)) as "expected_delivery_date" ,

            where YEAR(transaction_date) >= '2023' AND transaction_type IN ('Opportunity', 'Invoice', 'Sales Order', 'Journal Entry')
        )

        
),

data_consolidation AS 
(
    SELECT 
        t.* 
        , DENSE_RANK () OVER ( ORDER BY dbt_functional_snapshot_date DESC )                    AS snapshot_date_order
        , "hist_bu_code",
  "hist_bu_country_code",
  "hist_bu_currency",
  "hist_bu_legal_name",
  "hist_bu_commercial_group",
  "live_bu_code",
  "live_bu_country_code",
  "live_bu_currency",
  "live_bu_legal_name",
  "live_bu_commercial_group",
  "pk_bu_nsid",
  "bu_nsid"
        , COALESCE( fx_dated.fx_rate_original_to_usd, fx_latest.fx_rate_original_to_usd )            AS fx_rate_original_to_usd
        , COALESCE( fx_dated.fx_rate_original_to_dynamic, fx_latest.fx_rate_original_to_dynamic )    AS fx_rate_original_to_dynamic
        , 'EUR'                                                    AS dynamic_target_currency
    FROM union_current_and_snapshot t

    
    LEFT OUTER JOIN "netsuite"."prod_bus"."dim_bu" bu
        ON bu.pk_bu_nsid = t.fk_bu_nsid
        AND t.transaction_date BETWEEN bu.scd_valid_from_fill_date AND bu.scd_valid_to_fill_date

    
    LEFT OUTER JOIN "netsuite"."prod_bus"."fact_fx_avg_rate_latest" fx_latest
        ON bu.hist_bu_currency = fx_latest.original_currency
    LEFT OUTER JOIN "netsuite"."prod_bus"."fact_fx_avg_rate_dated" fx_dated
        ON bu.hist_bu_currency = fx_dated.original_currency
        AND EOMONTH(t.transaction_date) = fx_dated.closing_date
)

SELECT 
    * 
    , fx_rate_original_to_usd     * bu_amount AS usd_amount
    , fx_rate_original_to_dynamic * bu_amount AS dynamic_amount
FROM data_consolidation

  "fx_rate_original_to_usd",
  "fx_rate_original_to_dynamic",

    , CAST ( CASE WHEN t.transaction_type IN ('Opportunity', 'Sales Order') THEN t.expected_delivery_date ELSE t.transaction_date END AS DATE ) AS calculation_date
FROM "netsuite"."prod_bus"."fact_all_transactions_with_line" t 

WHERE t.transaction_type IN ( 'Opportunity', 'Invoice', 'Sales Order' )
AND
    ( 
        ( t.transaction_type NOT IN ('Opportunity', 'Sales Order') )
        OR 
        ( t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity' AND t.transaction_status IN ( 'Under Discussion', 'Ongoing' ) )
        OR
        ( t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order' AND t.transaction_status IN ( 'Under Discussion', 'Ongoing' ) )
    )
)


, cte_calculate AS (
SELECT 
    t.*
    
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1, bu_amount, 0) AS total_bu_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1, bu_amount, 0) AS total_bu_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1, bu_amount, 0) AS total_bu_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1, bu_amount, 0) AS total_bu_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
    
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1, usd_amount, 0) AS total_usd_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1, usd_amount, 0) AS total_usd_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1, usd_amount, 0) AS total_usd_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1, usd_amount, 0) AS total_usd_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
    
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1, dynamic_amount, 0) AS total_dynamic_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1, dynamic_amount, 0) AS total_dynamic_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1, dynamic_amount, 0) AS total_dynamic_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1, dynamic_amount, 0) AS total_dynamic_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
    
    
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', bu_amount, 0) AS opportunity_bu_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', bu_amount, 0) AS opportunity_bu_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', bu_amount, 0) AS opportunity_bu_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', bu_amount, 0) AS opportunity_bu_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', bu_amount, 0) AS invoice_bu_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', bu_amount, 0) AS invoice_bu_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', bu_amount, 0) AS invoice_bu_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', bu_amount, 0) AS invoice_bu_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', bu_amount, 0) AS sales_order_bu_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', bu_amount, 0) AS sales_order_bu_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', bu_amount, 0) AS sales_order_bu_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', bu_amount, 0) AS sales_order_bu_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
    
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', usd_amount, 0) AS opportunity_usd_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', usd_amount, 0) AS opportunity_usd_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', usd_amount, 0) AS opportunity_usd_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', usd_amount, 0) AS opportunity_usd_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', usd_amount, 0) AS invoice_usd_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', usd_amount, 0) AS invoice_usd_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', usd_amount, 0) AS invoice_usd_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', usd_amount, 0) AS invoice_usd_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', usd_amount, 0) AS sales_order_usd_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', usd_amount, 0) AS sales_order_usd_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', usd_amount, 0) AS sales_order_usd_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', usd_amount, 0) AS sales_order_usd_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
    
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', dynamic_amount, 0) AS opportunity_dynamic_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', dynamic_amount, 0) AS opportunity_dynamic_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', dynamic_amount, 0) AS opportunity_dynamic_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Opportunity', dynamic_amount, 0) AS opportunity_dynamic_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', dynamic_amount, 0) AS invoice_dynamic_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', dynamic_amount, 0) AS invoice_dynamic_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', dynamic_amount, 0) AS invoice_dynamic_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Invoice', dynamic_amount, 0) AS invoice_dynamic_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_2y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', dynamic_amount, 0) AS sales_order_dynamic_amount_prev_2y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_prev_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', dynamic_amount, 0) AS sales_order_dynamic_amount_prev_1y_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_current_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', dynamic_amount, 0) AS sales_order_dynamic_amount_current_fiscal_year
        , IIF(d_calc.is_next_1y_fiscal_year = 1 AND t.transaction_type = 'Sales Order', dynamic_amount, 0) AS sales_order_dynamic_amount_next_1y_fiscal_year
        
    
FROM cte_scope t 
LEFT OUTER JOIN "netsuite"."prod_bus"."dim_date" d_calc
    ON d_calc.pk_date_standard = t.calculation_date 
)
